            A filtering approach that only allows access to pre-approved websites. More restrictive but very secure.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-primary mb-2 dark:text-primary-400">Blacklist / Blocklist</h4>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-0">
            A filtering approach that blocks specific websites or categories while allowing everything else. Less
            restrictive but requires good filtering technology.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-primary mb-2 dark:text-primary-400">Screen Time</h4>
